Subject: Predefined Content is not getting blocked
Description:
Hello Team,

We are conducting a POC for one of our customers, Univest Stocking PTV LTD. The POC is nearing closure, with only two pending issues:

1. The Netwrix EPP certificate is not installed on web browsers. Additionally, the customer uses a device requiring biometric authentication (certificate-based) to access certain websites.
2. SSN and Tax ID for both text and images (OCR) is not working as expected.

We kindly request the support team to schedule a meeting with the customer to address these issues and expedite the POC closure.

Best regards,
Solution_Comment__c: Issue solved in the remote session
